      - But you're the one      
      that suggested it.        

50:43.408 --> 50:47.076
     - Well, I suggested it     
     because you like it.       

50:47.078 --> 50:49.745
      - Okay, then what         
      do you wanna watch?       

50:49.747 --> 50:51.814
   People kissing in the rain   
   or something like that?      

50:51.816 --> 50:52.715
             - No.              

51:15.139 --> 51:16.639
  - (Sighing) Okay, seriously.  

51:16.641 --> 51:18.107
      Are you ever gonna        
      put that thing down?      

51:18.109 --> 51:18.808
           - Um, no.            

51:53.444 --> 51:55.744
 - Hey, do you want my zip-up?  

51:55.746 --> 51:57.446
 - I'll just turn the heat up.  

51:57.448 --> 51:58.547
        - But it's hot.         

51:58.549 --> 52:01.450
- I'll just get a sweater then. 

52:01.452 --> 52:03.385
      - Okay, what's            
      with your attitude?       

52:03.387 --> 52:04.587
    - Sorry I'm not perfect!    

52:04.588 --> 52:05.788
     - You could just be        
     a little nicer to me.      

52:05.790 --> 52:07.389
       - Well, I can't          
       please everybody.        

52:07.391 --> 52:09.525
       - What? Okay, what       
       is your problem?         

52:09.527 --> 52:11.494
  - So now, I have a problem?   

52:11.496 --> 52:15.197
    - Look, that's not          
    what I said, it's just...   

52:15.199 --> 52:15.898
            God, um.            

52:17.902 --> 52:19.301
     Okay, how about this?      

52:19.303 --> 52:21.670
      How about I'll just       
      pause the movie           

52:21.672 --> 52:23.405
and you can go get your sweater?

52:23.407 --> 52:25.341
   - Don't bother, I'm just     
   gonna go to the darkroom.    

52:25.343 --> 52:26.909
     I've got stuff to do.      

52:26.911 --> 52:28.611
 - Wait, hold up. Stuff to do?  

52:28.613 --> 52:30.412
       What, is it more         
       important than me?       

52:30.414 --> 52:31.514
           - I guess.           

52:33.451 --> 52:34.550
        - Alright fine.         

52:34.552 --> 52:35.484
I guess I'm not important enough

52:35.486 --> 52:37.520
 to take you to the dance then. 

52:37.522 --> 52:39.022
            - What?             

52:39.023 --> 52:40.523
      - You heard me, I         
      said I'm not going.       

52:40.525 --> 52:42.892
      - [Belle] Stop, stop      
      being ridiculous.         

52:42.894 --> 52:45.294
- Really? 'Cause I was thinking 
the same thing about you.       

52:45.296 --> 52:46.629
- What's that supposed to mean? 

52:46.631 --> 52:48.597
- You can be so smart sometimes,

52:48.599 --> 52:51.267
       but yet, so dumb         
       at the same time.        

52:51.269 --> 52:52.535
    - I'm dumb? You're dumb.    

52:52.537 --> 52:54.603
    I'm not the one failing     
    out of high school.         

52:54.605 --> 52:56.605
   - I'm missing my math test   
   right now because of you.    

52:56.607 --> 52:57.573
          - Whatever.           

52:57.575 --> 52:59.687
          You're dumb!          

52:59.688 --> 53:01.800
     - I'm not dumb enough      
     to starve myself           

53:01.801 --> 53:03.913
and think that it's gonna bring 
my mommy back or something.     

53:10.922 --> 53:13.589
         (Belle crying)         

53:19.597 --> 53:20.829
    - [Automated Voice] Your    
    call has been forwarded     

53:20.831 --> 53:23.599
 to an automated voice message. 

54:09.313 --> 54:10.246
       (banging on door)        

54:10.248 --> 54:12.414
 - [Gus] Belle, open the door.  

54:12.416 --> 54:13.882
 Belle, come on, open the door. 

54:13.884 --> 54:15.618
      - I'm fine, get out!      

54:36.941 --> 54:40.976
   - Come on, Belle, open the   
   (screaming)                  

54:40.978 --> 54:42.378
         - [Belle] Mom.         

54:42.380 --> 54:45.514
     - [Belle's Dad] No         
     sweetie, it's just me.     

55:13.878 --> 55:15.477
          - I'm sorry.          

55:15.479 --> 55:19.581
   - [Belle's Dad] It's         
   okay. It's okay, sweetie.    

55:22.687 --> 55:24.520
     - I really messed up.      

55:26.824 --> 55:28.490
       - You're perfect.        

55:34.498 --> 55:37.499
       (foreboding music)       

55:44.975 --> 55:46.608
           - Hey Gus.           

55:46.610 --> 55:47.993
       - [Gus] Hey Lyla.        

55:47.994 --> 55:49.377
    - I heard you were going    
    to the dance with Belle.    

55:49.380 --> 55:50.546
   - Okay look, I don't have    
   time for this right now.     

55:50.548 --> 55:52.514
    - Where is Belle anyway?    

55:52.516 --> 55:53.549
    - Don't worry about it.     

55:53.550 --> 55:54.583
      - [Lyla] Wasn't           
      she with you today?       

55:54.585 --> 55:55.451
     - Well yeah, she was.      

55:55.453 --> 55:57.553
    - [Lyla] Another fight?     

55:57.555 --> 55:58.987
     - Why don't you just       
     stay out of it, okay?      

55:58.989 --> 56:00.556
       - That's not what        
       you usually say.         

56:00.558 --> 56:01.890
       - [Gus] What do          
       you want from me?        

56:01.892 --> 56:03.092
   - Just a concerned friend.   

56:03.094 --> 56:05.828
         (Gus scoffing)         

56:10.434 --> 56:12.534
     - [Gus] Look Mr. Davy,     
     we need to talk, okay?     

56:12.536 --> 56:13.369
         - Gus, right.          

56:13.371 --> 56:14.036
    I heard a lot about you.    

56:14.038 --> 56:15.471
     - [Gus] One and only.      

56:15.473 --> 56:16.661
       - Look, I'm sorry.       

56:16.662 --> 56:17.850
      I don't have time         
      for whatever trouble      

56:17.851 --> 56:19.039
     you've gotten              
     yourself into now, I--     

56:19.043 --> 56:21.610
   - Just give me two           
   minutes, just two minutes.   

56:21.612 --> 56:23.712
   - Don't they have            
   counselors over at Briary?   

56:23.714 --> 56:25.080
       I really don't           
       have time to spare       

56:25.082 --> 56:27.015
       for any of you           
       boys, I apologize.       

56:27.017 --> 56:28.550
     - Yeah, that's right.      

56:28.552 --> 56:30.819
    Focus most of your time     
    on these ladies, huh?       

56:30.821 --> 56:32.020
          - Excuse me?          

56:32.022 --> 56:33.622
       That was extremely       
       disrespectful.           

56:33.624 --> 56:35.124
         (Gus scoffing)         
         Hey.                   

56:35.126 --> 56:38.460
   I take my job seriously.     
   I worked very hard for it.   

56:38.462 --> 56:40.496
      - Okay look, I know       
      you don't like me,        

56:40.498 --> 56:43.799
     right back at ya, this     
     is very important.         

56:46.637 --> 56:47.836
      - What do you mean?       

56:47.838 --> 56:48.637
    - Belle, I've scheduled     
    a follow-up meeting         

56:48.639 --> 56:50.406
     with the nurse today.      

56:50.408 --> 56:51.774
    I'd appreciate it if you    
    saw her after school.       

56:51.776 --> 56:53.976
   - But I'm supposed to help   

56:53.978 --> 56:55.944
      set up for the            
      dance after school.       

56:55.946 --> 56:57.179
- Without a pass from the nurse,

56:57.181 --> 57:01.183
    you won't even be           
    allowed into the dance.     

57:01.185 --> 57:02.618
         School policy.         

57:05.956 --> 57:07.156
   (cellphone alert beeping)    

57:07.158 --> 57:09.124
      - Did you steal           
      those from the gym?       

57:09.126 --> 57:10.526
     - I'll give them back.     

57:10.528 --> 57:12.961
     - [Brunette Girl]          
     That's not the point.      

57:12.963 --> 57:14.530
     - [Lyla] Drink plenty      
     of water to add weight     

57:14.532 --> 57:16.598
    without adding calories.    

57:20.604 --> 57:22.438
       - I can't believe        
       we're doing this.        

57:22.440 --> 57:23.639
      - I find it quite         
      admirable, actually.      

57:23.641 --> 57:24.673
   - [Brunette Girl] Olivia!    

57:24.675 --> 57:26.208
            - What?             

57:26.210 --> 57:28.610
  If I can't go to the dance,   
  we might as well help Belle.  

57:28.612 --> 57:29.845
- Why can't you go to the dance?

57:29.847 --> 57:31.547
 - You failed math, didn't you? 

57:31.549 --> 57:33.048
  - [Brunette Girl] Whatever.   

57:33.050 --> 57:34.950
      Like, as soon as          
      this dance is over,       

57:34.952 --> 57:36.785
 you have to eat something and  

57:36.787 --> 57:38.787
     we'll get you help and     
     we'll tell someone.        

57:38.789 --> 57:40.489
     - [Belle] No, I'm          
     fine, stay out of it.      

57:40.491 --> 57:42.624
   - [Olivia] I don't think     
   that's an option anymore.    

57:42.626 --> 57:45.761
      - Why don't you just      
      eat something now?        

57:46.797 --> 57:49.631
      - Really, I'm okay,       
      and thank you.            

57:52.203 --> 57:55.571
      Okay, now give me         
      all of your change.       

58:08.586 --> 58:10.486
     - [Nurse] Have a seat.     

58:17.194 --> 58:18.627
        - Alright class.        

58:18.629 --> 58:21.897
    I'd like to congratulate    
    a very special student      

58:21.899 --> 58:24.900
      for getting into the      
      Columbia program.         

58:24.902 --> 58:27.603
     I'd like to share that     
     Lyla has been accepted     

58:27.605 --> 58:28.837
    and will be taking part     

58:28.839 --> 58:30.072
    in this great               
    opportunity this summer.    

58:30.074 --> 58:31.607
      So let's go ahead         
      and give her a hand.      

58:31.609 --> 58:34.610
       (class applauding)       

58:37.748 --> 58:40.115
    - Do I need to undress.     

58:40.117 --> 58:42.184
    - [Nurse] Not necessary.    

58:47.858 --> 58:51.226
      - So will I be able       
      to go to the dance?       

58:51.228 --> 58:54.663
     (school bell ringing)      

58:59.803 --> 59:01.570
            Hey Gus.            

59:01.572 --> 59:02.771
        I'm sorry again.        

59:04.008 --> 59:06.909
       Can we please go         
       together tonight?        

59:07.745 --> 59:08.644
            Call me.            

59:13.083 --> 59:17.185
   (cellphone alert beeping)    

59:17.187 --> 59:19.755
         (Gus sighing)          

01:00:00.130 --> 01:00:01.363
   - I can do your hair next.   

01:00:01.365 --> 01:00:05.000
    - Nah, I think I'm just     
    gonna leave it alone.       

01:00:08.872 --> 01:00:11.106
   - Since when do you smoke?   

01:00:11.108 --> 01:00:12.808
      - Helps with nerves.      

01:00:12.810 --> 01:00:15.344
       - [Lyla] What are        
       you nervous about?       

01:00:15.346 --> 01:00:17.312
      - And it doesn't          
      make me that hungry.      

01:00:17.314 --> 01:00:18.747
         - There we go.         

01:00:38.268 --> 01:00:41.169
       Is that from the         
       Columbia program?        

01:00:42.806 --> 01:00:45.374
  I thought you didn't apply.   

01:00:45.376 --> 01:00:46.375
          - I didn't.           

01:00:52.349 --> 01:00:54.016
       - Did you get in?        

01:01:00.991 --> 01:01:01.890
            Course.             

01:01:03.293 --> 01:01:04.860
       What do you think?       

01:01:08.732 --> 01:01:10.365
         - Looks great.         

01:01:10.367 --> 01:01:13.168
       - Try yours on so        
       we can compare.          

01:01:34.324 --> 01:01:36.158
      - I can't wear this.      

01:01:36.160 --> 01:01:37.426
       - [Lyla] Why not?        

01:01:38.896 --> 01:01:40.362
   - I don't like it anymore.   

01:01:40.364 --> 01:01:42.798
     I think I'm just gonna     
     wear something else.       

01:01:42.800 --> 01:01:45.467
    - You spent all your        
    allowance on that dress.    

01:01:45.469 --> 01:01:47.402
 Isn't that why you've been     
 practically starving yourself? 

01:01:47.404 --> 01:01:48.837
            - What?             

01:01:48.839 --> 01:01:49.805
              No.               

01:01:49.807 --> 01:01:51.073
I mean, yeah, I used the money, 

01:01:51.075 --> 01:01:53.742
but I didn't do it for a dress. 

01:01:55.713 --> 01:01:56.478
          - Then why?           

01:01:57.314 --> 01:01:58.780
            For Gus?            

01:01:58.782 --> 01:01:59.481
           - For me.            

01:02:00.818 --> 01:02:01.717
             - Oh.              

01:02:03.387 --> 01:02:06.722
       Well, just throw a       
       jacket on over it.       

01:02:10.461 --> 01:02:14.496
      (dance music)             
      (students chatting)       

